ifikasi otomatis yang dikirimkan TriPay ke server Mitra saat status transaksi berubah (terutama saat pembayaran berhasil). Halaman ini menjelaskan cara kerja, konfigurasi, dan penanganan callback.",[221,222],"hr",{},[224,225,227],"h2",{"id":226},"pengertian-callbackipn","Pengertian Callback/IPN",[209,229,230,232,233,236],{},[212,231,218],{}," adalah HTTP request yang dikirimkan oleh server TriPay ke URL yang ditentukan oleh Mitra untuk memberitahukan perubahan status transaksi secara ",[212,234,235],{},"real-time",".",[238,239,241],"h3",{"id":240},"fungsi-callback","Fungsi Callback",[243,244,246],"list",{"type":245},"info",[247,248,249,257,264,273],"ul",{},[250,251,252,253,256],"li",{},"Memberitahu Mitra bahwa pembayaran telah ",[212,254,255],{},"berhasil"," (PAID)",[250,258,259,260,263],{},"Memungkinkan Mitra untuk ",[212,261,262],{},"update status pesanan"," secara otomatis",[250,265,266,267,269,270],{},"Mendukung proses bisnis yang ",[212,268,235],{}," dan ",[212,271,272],{},"otomatis",[250,274,275],{},"Mengurangi kebutuhan pengecekan manual",[221,277],{},[224,279,281],{"id":280},"cara-kerja-callback","Cara Kerja Callback",[238,283,285],{"id":284},"alur-proses","Alur Proses",[287,288,293],"pre",{"className":289,"code":291,"language":292},[290],"language-text","1. Pelanggan Melakukan Pembayaran\n              ↓\n2. Pembayaran Diverifikasi oleh PJP Rekanan\n              ↓\n3. Status Transaksi Berubah ke PAID di Sistem TriPay\n              ↓\n4. TriPay Mengirim HTTP POST ke Callback URL Mitra\n              ↓\n5. Server Mitra Menerima dan Memproses Data\n              ↓\n6. Server Mitra Mengembalikan Response (JSON)\n              ↓\n7. Mitra Update Status Pesanan di Sistem Internal\n","text",[294,295,291],"code",{"__ignoreMap":296},"",[238,298,300],{"id":299},"kapan-callback-dikirim","Kapan Callback Dikirim?",[302,303,304,317],"table",{},[305,306,307],"thead",{},[308,309,310,314],"tr",{},[311,312,313],"th",{},"Event",[311,315,316],{},"Callback Dikirim",[318,319,3